102 template<typename value_t, typename id_t, typename value_no_cv_t>
103 __PSI_REFERENCE__ PiercedStorageIterator<value_t, id_t, value_no_cv_t>::getValue(std::size_t k) const
104 {
105  if (*this == m_storage->getKernel().end()) {
106  throw std::out_of_range("Iterator points to an invalid position.");
107  }
108 
109  std::size_t rawIndex = getRawIndex();
110 
111  return m_storage->rawAt(rawIndex, k);
112 }
